LICENSE INFORMATION

vAmiga consists of three major parts:

1. The vAmiga application (as provided by this repository)
2. The core Amiga emulator (everything inside directory `Emulator`)
3. The CPU emulator (everything inside directory `Emulator/CPU/Moira`)

The top-level license of the vAmiga project is the GNU General Public License v3. The two subcomponents listed above are published under more liberate terms. In detail:

Component 1: vAmiga application
    License: GPL-3.0-or-later
             https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

Component 2: Core emulator
    License: MPL-2.0
             https://mozilla.org/MPL/2.0

Component 3: CPU emulator (Moira)
    License: MIT
